    "To address these issues, researchers have developed automatic ANA detection methods, which have gained significant attention.",
    "Based on datasets, previous studies can be categorized into cell-level [1], [2], [9] and specimen-level ANA detection [42], [43].Most methods focus on cell-level detection, which involves analyzing single-cell images.",
